_sText:
This is my 4th released map.

It takes place in one of those self-storage compounds. (In this case a high security one because for 46 lockers there are 2 offices and 2 guard stations)

The entire map is as mirrored as I could make it but it's off by a few small, unimportant inches. Of the 46 lockers the players can get into 6 of the 8 open ones. There is access to the rooftops but there is little cover there. In addition there are a few vehicles.

STORY:
I guess you can't have much of a story when it comes to FY_ maps but I can imagine that the Ts have broken into the compound in an attempt to steal something.
